job.title: C# Developer

customFields.generatedDescriptionAI:
We are looking for a skilled C# Developer to join our team for a project that is expected to last more than 6 months. The ideal candidate should have a strong background in .NET Framework, ASP.NET, and Microsoft SQL Server. Experience with API integration, Windows App Development, and desktop application development is also required. Proficiency in C++ and C is a plus. 

As a C# Developer, your main responsibility will be to develop and maintain high-quality software applications using C# programming language. You will work closely with our team to understand project requirements and translate them into functional code. Additionally, you will be responsible for debugging and resolving any issues that arise during the development process. 

To apply for this position, please submit a proposal detailing how you can contribute to this project. We also encourage you to include links to any relevant past projects that showcase your skills and experience.
